.specify/
specs/


# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Flowchad (Fellowship-dev)
# https://github.com/Fellowship-dev/flowchad
# Drop-in AI QA auditor. .flowchad/ contains skills, commands, flow
# definitions, snapshots, and reports. All generated output is gitignored
# within .flowchad/ itself (snapshots/, reports/).
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
.flowchad/


# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Vercel Skills CLI
# https://github.com/vercel-labs/skills
# Cross-agent skill package manager. .agents/ is the canonical centralized
# location for skills shared across agents. The CLI symlinks from each agent's
# skill directory (e.g. .claude/skills/, .cursor/skills/) into .agents/skills/.
# skills-lock.json tracks installed versions.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
.agents/
skills-lock.json


